      "text": "クリスマスライブに向けて練習にも熱が入っているな\n……しかし、いつもより動きが硬い気がするが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You are really enthusiastic about the Christmas live practice.\n…But it feels like your movements are stiffer than usual…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.5,
