      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、調子が良くないようだが何かあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work. It seems something's bothering you. Anything wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、少し疲れが溜まっているのかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry. I might be a little tired.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "今度、学校でクリスマス会をやるんですが\n私も生徒会長として手伝うことになったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm also helping organize a Christmas event\nat school this time as the student council president.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "ライブの練習、生徒会の通常業務、期末テストの勉強\nそれにクリスマス会の準備で休む暇がなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Between the live practice‚ student council duties‚ studying for finals‚\nand preparing for the Christmas event‚ I haven't had any free time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか。あまり無理しないようにな\nもし俺に手伝えることがあれば遠慮なく言ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Don't push yourself too hard.\nIf there's anything I can help with‚ feel free to let me know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
